rders]]\n|March 29, 2019\n|-\n|3\n|The Suspicious Case of the [[Gu\u00f0mundur and Geirfinnur case|Reykjavik Confessions]]\n|April 5, 2019\n|-\n|4\n|The Unexplained Murder of [[Bugsy Siegel]]\n|April 12, 2019\n|-\n|5\n|The Horrifying [[Texarkana Moonlight Murders|Texarkana Phantom Killer]]\n|April 19, 2019\n|-\n|6\n|The Shocking [[Athalia Ponsell Lindsley|Florida Machete Murder]]\n|April 26, 2019\n|-\n|7\n|The Puzzling [[Christine Collins#Disappearance of Walter Collins|Disappearance of Walter Collins]]\n|May 3, 2019\n|-\n|8\n|The Curious [[Death of Vincent Van Gogh]]\n|May 10, 2019\n|-\n|9\n|The Impossible [[Disappearance of Dorothy Arnold]]\n|September 26, 2019\n|-\n|}\n\n==== Season 6 ====\n{| class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\"\n!#\n!Episode\n!Published\n|-\n|1\n|The Macabre [[Death of Edgar Allan Poe]]\n|March 13, 2020\n|-\n|2\n|The Missing Identity of The [[Lady of the Dunes]]\n|March 20, 2020\n|-\n|3\n|The Tinseltown Murder Of [[Thelma Todd]]\n|March 27, 2020\n|-\n|4\n|The Creepy Quandary of [[Who put Bella in the Wych Elm?|Who Put Bella in the Wych Elm]]\n|April 3, 2020\n|-\n|5\n|The Puzzling Case of Marilyn and [[Sam Sheppard]]\n|April 10, 2020\n|}\n\n===BuzzFeed Unsolved \u2013 Supernatural===\n\n==== Season 1 ====\n{| class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\"\n!#\n!Episode\n!Published\n|-\n|1\n|The Creepy Real-Life \"[[Men In Black]]\"\n|April 29, 2016\n|-\n|2\n|The Secret Society Of The [[Illuminati]]\n|July 29, 2016\n|-\n|3\n|3 Horrifying Cases Of Ghosts and Demons\n|October 26, 2016\n|-\n|4\n|The Chilling Exorcism Of [[Anneliese Michel]]\n|November 12, 2016\n|-\n|5\n|The Bizarre Toxic [[Death of Gloria Ramirez]]\n|December 3, 2016\n|-\n|6\n|The Spirits Of The [[Whaley House (San Diego, California)|Whaley House]]\n|January 13, 2017\n|-\n|7\n|The Haunted Decks of the [[RMS Queen Mary|Queen Mary]]\n|February 17, 2017\n|}\n\n==== Season 2 ====\n{| class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\"\n!#\n!Episode\n!Published\n|-\n|1\n|The Ghos